**Designed for** - Employers of all types - Stakeholders whose accountabilities include productivity / economic development - Insurers to reduce claims: health, accident, worker comp, negligence - Educational providers: pupil / students - Healthcare: patients partners - Lifestyle, gyms, hospitality: wellness without walls

Otto.bot Otto.bot for Microsoft Teams provides business customers and managed service providers (MSPs) with an Artificial Intelligence (AI) help desk and IT support chatbot to automate various IT, HR, and RPA tasks. You can diagnose a slow-running pc, automate manual data entries for legacy software, allow users to request time off. Users can customize the bot according to organizational needs and can be tailored to target complex scenarios.
- Interact with the bot using Natural Language queries
- Automate repetitive tasks such as opening tickets, answering QnA
- Run RPA skills using Power Automate or equivalent resources
- Handle user permissions using multiple roles and departments
**_Limitations_** - The **Connect to Kaseya**, **Connect to Microsoft** features are currently only supported on [App Portal](https://app.otto.bot).
You can also get started by signing up for a new account at [https://otto.bot](https://otto.bot) or [https://app.otto.bot](https://app.otto.bot).

g.aria-label: iInsights iInsights is a powerful app that provides users with easy access to their Power BI reports from within the Microsoft Teams environment. The app offers several main features, including seamless integration with Power BI, support for RLS data isolation, and an embedded chatbot that can help users quickly navigate to their desired reports. One of the major problems iInsights solves is the need for users to switch between different applications to access their Power BI reports. With this app, users can simply launch it from within their Microsoft Teams environment and view all the reports they have access to without leaving the Teams interface. The target audience for this app is anyone who uses Microsoft Teams and has a valid licensed Power BI account. This app is ideal for business professionals, data analysts, and other users who need to work with data and analysis on a regular basis. It can be used in a variety of industries, including finance, healthcare, retail, and more. It is important to note that there are a few limitations to the functionality of this app. Users must have a valid licensed Power BI account and their credentials must be the same as their Microsoft Teams account. Additionally, the app only displays the reports that the user has access to, so users must have appropriate permissions to view the reports they want to see. Users must purchase a valid subscription plan to enjoy all the features of iInsights. For any further assistance reach out to us at ticket@innominds.com Add

PowerRoster for Frontline PowerRoster for Frontline is a planning & scheduling solution for organizations with diverse workforces. It reduces manual handling on employee allocation and assignment of staff and contractors to rostered work patterns and shifts and makes it easy for the Frontline workers to access get visibility of their upcoming assignments.
PowerRoster for Frontline app allows organizations to provide a unified view of the shifts and schedule for the workforce, ask for a change in schedule, swap the shift or take shifts from the available roster.
Whether planning the shift patterns for Nurses, Care Workers, Police Officers or First Responders, Field Technicians, Production Operators or Emergency Response Crews, PowerRoster provides a simple intuitive interface for the organization to manage the shifts/rosters for the workforce. Some key features of the application are :
Provide visibility for the staffing need and resource allocation Simple dashboard view for the Frontline workers to manage upcoming shifts Empower Frontline workers to swap shifts Optimize workforce availability Forecast upcoming shifts across multiple rosters
**Availability** In order to use this app, your organization will require PowerRoster admin access and license to create and manage rosters for the frontline workers. Please submit your details via the [Contact us](https://powerroster.com/contact/) our team will assist you. New to PowerRoster for Frontline? [Contact us](https://powerroster.com/contact/) by filling in your details and our Support team will contact you to get the PowerRoster configured for your organization. Add

Simple In/Out Keeping track of your staff has never been so easy. No electronic in/out board software supports more platforms, provides more options for updating your status, or makes your life easier than Simple In/Out.
View your colleagues all in one place. Our board displays names, statuses, comments, and more. Use search to quickly find users. Sort your board by multiple columns to see everyone in the order you prefer. Clicking on a user provides their contact details so you'll never need a company directory ever again.
Using our connector, all your Simple In/Out status updates can be sent to the group messaging channel of your choosing. Your Simple In/Out board is also viewable within Microsoft Teams via our tab. You never have to leave Microsoft Teams to see your entire board.
When your status within Microsoft Teams changes, we can update your Simple In/Out status to match. Our integration allows your Microsoft Teams presence information to be available within Simple In/Out, and allows you to take advantage of all the Simple In/Out features we offer like Notifications. With free Bright Remind Me, you can: - Set reminders for messages - Set custom text reminders - Snooze reminders - Monthly reminder limits apply With a paid plan, you can also: - Get unlimited reminders - Individual and team options available

ClassCred *Education gamified: Incentives beyond grades*
Increase engagement and manage your course. Use gamification and peer recognition to keep students engaged and connected. Easy-to-use tools streamline course management and allow you to stay focused on educating.
*Key features*
*Polls:* Solicit feedback from your students and reward for participating *Debates:* Kick off discussions and let students compete *Questions:* Track student questions and let the class pick the best answers *Announcements:* Schedule announcements and reward for acknowledging *Assignments:* Instructor and peer reviewed assignments *Peer recognition:* Students reward each other's contributions *Levels:* Achievement levels encourage participation *Store:* Students redeem points for items in the class store. Sell study guides, bonus points, endorsements, or anything else you dream up.
*Manage your course* Real time dashboards and analytics Roles for instructors and students Import and export data to integrate with your LMS
Optimized for higher education and business
For more information, please visit [classcred.com](https://classcred.com) or email [support@classcred.com](mailto:support@classcred.com) Add

- Review recent Notes and Communications. The Matter Dashboard tab makes it easy to review recent updates to your matters. - Plan for upcoming events. Whether you need to seamlessly coordinate with your team for spontaneous brainstorming sessions or stay informed about team members planning to work from the office, the Robin Microsoft Teams app is your go-to solution. Leveraging real-time analytics, it ensures that every square foot of your workspace promotes employee productivity and engagement, adapting to evolving work dynamics across the entire organization. ShareGate ShareGate's the companion app for end users to collaborate with IT pros, at scale, to create and manage their teams. That way, everyone is equipped to their best work in Microsoft 365.
Reduce your support ticket queue. Say goodbye to guessing games and chasing owners for answers.
Be proactive and delegate the creation and ongoing management of teams to those who create and use themyour users!
With ShareGate, they get to: * See and manage all their teams, including the ones they own, in a centralized place * Create new teams from IT approved provisioning templates * Automatically receive bot notifications once a team is no longer active to archive, delete or keep
* Regularly clean up externally shared links and guests * Classify teams by purpose and sensitivity with tags you customize
Keeping your tenant organized and secure is everyones business!
Note that for our app to function as intended, your organization will need to obtain a license for ShareGate. Learn more here: [https://sharegate.com/pricing](https://sharegate.com/pricing) Add

DailyBot DailyBot is an AI and ChatGPT powered assistant that provides an all-in-one toolkit for Microsoft Teams. Replace unnecessary meetings with daily standups or automated team check-ins. Improve team interactions with kudos, virtual coffees, and watercoolers, or automate workflows with in-chat forms and custom chat commands.
Thousands of startups and enterprises use DailyBot to improve team collaboration and agile development practices. Backed by Y Combinator
DailyBot works with Microsoft Teams by typing: @DailyBot in a channel or group chat Sending a direct message to DailyBot.
** CHECK-INS**
Use standup check-ins to stay in sync with your team.
Try these commands in your chat to see everything you can do with **_checkin_**.
Type **_checkin_** in a direct message to start your check-in update. Type **_checkin status_** in a direct message to get the status of your check-ins. Type **_checkin reset_** to remove your report from a check-in. Type **_checkin edit_** in a direct message to edit your check-in responses.
** KUDOS**
Give kudos and create a great company culture. When you create a culture of appreciation, you help employees feel valued and equipped to succeed.
Try these commands in your chat to see everything you can do with **_kudos_**. Type **_kudos to_** **@user1 @user2 {message}** to give kudos, the message is optional. Type **_kudos leaderboard_** or **_kudos top_** to see your organization's kudos leaderboard. Type **_kudos status_** or **_kudos me_** to get a summary of your kudos history.
** VIRTUAL COFFEE**
A lot of startups and big companies are realizing the value of virtual coffees. This informal networking event can be anything from a Zoom call to a talk over Microsoft Teams.
It shouldn't be surprising that, when done well, virtual coffees lead to better communication and, ultimately, better product decisions among teammates.
Type **_virtual coffee_** to participate in weekly matches for 1-1s and casual conversations.
** WATERCOOLER**
Water cooler chat is the simplest way to relax at work. The *watercooler* command sends conversation starters automatically to a channel (of your choice) where anyone can come and weigh in.
Type **_watercooler_** to set up automatic water cooler questions somewhere in the chat (public and private channels)
** BIRTHDAY**
One doesn't need many reasons to celebrate life in all its splendor. One-on-one recognition can go a long way, from boosting employee engagement to increasing happiness and productivity.
Type **_birthday_** to automate birthday reminders and notifications in the workplace.
** MATCH**
Using an onboarding process that fosters positive working relationships will help new employees build confidence and become productive quickly.
Type **_match_** to automate 1:1 intros between the team and new collaborators.
** POMODORO**
The Pomodoro Technique is a simple, yet effective time management method. Run pomodoro sessions in the chat with custom alerts.
Type **_pomodoro_** to start a session.
** COUNTDOWN**
A countdown can be a good way to motivate yourself to do something you might otherwise put off. For example, if you are working towards a goal, a countdown can help you remember to do it every day.
Type **_countdown_** to set a daily countdown to an important milestone.
** GENERAL COMMANDS**
Type **_dashboard_** to get direct access to the web app. Type **_news_** to see whats new on DailyBot. Type **_time_** to get your current time settings. Type **_feedback_** to send us your comments or suggestions.
For more information or to contact the DailyBot team visit our [support center ](https://help.dailybot.com/). Add

Ideanote With Ideanote you can engage your people in innovation and efficiently manage ideas right inside Microsoft Teams.
Collect, develop and prioritize ideas with a powerful platform that offers the structure and process you need to innovate faster and more effectively. Thoughtworks, Stanford and 2.000+ other businesses of all sizes - from small teams to Enterprises - use Ideanote to make ideas matter.
The Ideanote for Teams integration is built in collaboration with Microsoft.
**Easy Setup** 1. Add Ideanote to the Sidebar 2. Click 'Connect Ideanote with Microsoft Teams' on behalf of all tenant users 3. Login to your Ideanote workspace as an admin or create a new workspace. 4. Add Ideanote to channels or tabs where you work with ideas.
Trial available, unpaid plan available, support included.
**Use Cases** * *Idea Campaigns* - launch idea challenges on specific topics. * *Idea Management* - collect, develop, evaluate and track ideas. * *Employee Engagement* - engage employees in shaping the future of your business and make them feel part of something bigger. * *Continuous Improvement* - use Ideanote for lean, agile or kaizen workflows that let you spot and implement incremental improvements, * *Brainstorming* - real-time ideation during meetings, video calls or asynchronous with remote teams. * *Open Innovation* - involve customers, partners or external stakeholders in submitting solutions. * *Innovation Management* - manage your innovation portfolio with advanced ROI analytics.
**How it works:** 1. Create an idea collection for example on 'Cost Saving'. 2. Invite people or groups to submit ideas, comment, vote and more. 3. See ideas flowing in and the best ideas bubbling to the top. 4. Implement ideas and track your impact. 5. Add automations and integrations to save time.
**Features** * Idea Collections * Custom Idea Form Fields * Search, Sort and Filter Ideas * Share, Like, Comment, Rate, Assign, Review * Innovation Funnel * Drag & Drop Kanban * Custom Views incl. List View * Bulk Actions * Hidden Ideas & Activities * Anonymous Ideas * Tags and Mentions * Status Labels * Video Upload and Attachments * Access, Permissions and Roles * User Groups * Real-Time Notifications * Works on Mobile (iOS and Android) * Custom Evaluation and Prioritization * Leaderboard and Gamification * Insights, Trends and ROI Analytics * XLSX. Exports * 100+ Integrations * Automations * Translation of Ideas * Idea Linking * Visual Idea Cluster * AI Duplicate Detection across Languages * AI Suggestions and Idea Generation * Custom Branding * Custom Fonts and Colors, Domain * SSO Single Sign-On * Microsoft Power Automate
**Languages and Benefits** Available in Spanish (captura de ideas), French (recueillir des ides), German (ideen sammeln), Italian (raccogliere idee), Portuguese (coletar ideias), Dutch (ideen verzamelen), Finnish, Swedish, Norwegian, Danish, Hungarian, Czech, Korean, Japanese, Vietnamese, Thai and Simplified Chinese.
Used by Teams, Early Stage, Startups, Mid-Market and Enterprise in Leadership, Customer Success, Sales, Consulting, Retail, Healthcare, Manufacturing, Nonprofits, Education and more.
Companies use Ideanote to identify challenges, reduce costs, invent products, achieve strategic goals, stay resilient in times of crisis, master digital transformation and lead with a better customer experience.
